Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{=15}---- Dialogue
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.52,0:00:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.90,0:00:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The contents of the report are accurate.\nWe accept full responsibility for our mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.45,0:00:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.49,0:00:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.70,0:00:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! In one week?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.03,0:00:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, not at all. We will take care of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.46,0:00:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, do you want go fight those Abydos kids again?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.08,0:00:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We already blew all our cash, though.\nWhat's the plan this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.09,0:00:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're {\i1}already{\i0} strapped for cash\nbecause renting this office costs a fortune.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.34,0:00:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.97,0:00:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A company without a proper office\nis no company at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.43,0:00:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, I'm perfectly happy to go back\nto pitching some tents in the park.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.02,0:00:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I would follow you to the ends of the earth, {*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.77,0:00:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you all just be quiet?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.15,0:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking out a loan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.98,0:00:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I thought you were blacklisted from all the banks?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.90,0:00:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.78,0:00:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just been declared a wanted criminal\nand had my assets frozen, that's all!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, that was it!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.87,0:00:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.45,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll finish the mission, whatever it takes!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.80,0:02:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for choosing Kaiser Loans!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.01,0:02:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cash payment of 7,883,250 yen\nhas been duly recorded.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.39,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again next month!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.11,0:02:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it through another month, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.07,0:02:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why they only accept cash.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.32,0:03:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point. It would be much faster to transfer\nthe money from a bank account instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.12,0:03:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No attacking the transport car, Shiroko{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.75,0:03:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.67,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's begin our regular meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.92,0:03:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, about the part\nwe recovered the other day.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.55,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked into it, and it turns out it did in fact\noriginate from the Black Market.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.59,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Market is a dangerous place\nthat falls outside the jurisdiction of the GSC.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.47,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's become notorious for its illegal dealings\nand being a hotbed for unauthorised club activity.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.56,0:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(66,316,\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}It appears Problem Solver 68 frequents the area as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Problem Solver 68...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.53,0:03:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Helmet Gang was one thing,\nbut now these girls are after our school too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.45,0:03:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Given how often we're being raided,\nthere's gotta be more to the story.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why they're doing this.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.96,0:03:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.79,0:03:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigating the connection\nmight help us discover the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guess that settles it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a little field trip!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We got new guns on display. Check 'em out!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, for real?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.56,0:04:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so wild.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the Black Market.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all these people!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.23,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised such a large place\nhas flown under the GSC's radar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.23,0:04:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you only think that because\nwe're always holed up in Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange places like this exist all over the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.74,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been here before, {*}Hoshino{*Senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, this is my first time, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.50,0:04:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I hear, every district\nhas its share of wacky places.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.46,0:04:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently some schools even have huge aquariums.\nI hear they've got whales and stuff! {## addition to tie into her character story and because redundancy sucks}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to go one of these days.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That sounds nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.72,0:04:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay sharp, everyone. There's no telling\nwhat could happen out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.97,Alt,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Comment: 10,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hifumi noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.69,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit runnin' already!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please, leave me alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As if!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's have some fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.40,0:05:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't sound like it'd be much fun for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That uniform...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she from Trinity?
Comment: 10,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hifumi noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.58,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get behind me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, uh, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off, losers. We got business with the girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.13,0:05:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That chick's from Trinity.\nY'know, the most loaded school in Kivotos?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.14,0:05:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just gonna borrow her for a bit\nand ask for a little money in return!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.72,0:05:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch and release. Pretty slick, don't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.02,0:05:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say? Want in on this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll split the ransom—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.74,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you for saving me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.41,0:05:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ajitani Hifumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi{**-chan}, huh? Pleasure to meetcha!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.46,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I gotta ask, what brings a high-class girl\nfrom Trinity to this sketchy part of town?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually looking for something.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.51,0:06:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no longer being sold in stores,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.26,0:06:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I hear you can still find it here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Parts? Like for a tank?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,An illegal firearm, perhaps?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, maybe a biochemical weapon?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.73,0:06:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, no, nothing like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.23,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, uhh...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Limited-edition Peroro{**-sama} merch.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.61,0:06:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Peroro?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this handsome guy right here!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.28,0:06:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a super-limited-run Peroro{**-sama} plush.\nOnly one hundred units were ever produced!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.91,0:06:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's from Momo Friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I love that franchise!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Peroro{**-chan}'s just the cutest!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You like him too?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.79,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, this is way past my time.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what brings you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're also looking for something.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.18,0:06:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something that's easy to find,\nbut we heard it might be here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Guess we're in the same boat, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.35,0:06:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like your shopping trip\ntook a rather nasty turn, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.52,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, I knew this place was bad news.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.86,0:07:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And with the GSC's absence, corporations moved in\nand have been up to all kinds of mischief.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.33,0:07:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's apparently gotten so out of hand,\nthey even have their own bank and security now.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.87,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, that's gotta be highly illegal, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.25,0:07:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that the security here is especially dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.01,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Hifumi{**-chan}, you sure know your stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that settles it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.81,0:07:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We scratched your back, so now it's time you scratch ours\nand help us find what we're looking for!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.15,0:07:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we want a loan from {\i1}these{\i0} guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.36,0:07:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the shady Black Market bank, you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The interest rates must be a-astronomical...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.99,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's be real. Aru{**-chan} won't even pass\nthe background check anyway!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.08,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shut it! Of course I'll pass!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.50,0:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd. There should be {\i1}some{\i0} information\nabout your illegal part, but I can't find anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.18,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No transaction records. No storage logs...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.72,0:08:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost as if someone\nwent to great lengths to hide it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So someone is trying to cover it up?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.73,0:08:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.94,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The corporations run this place, but even they\nshouldn't be able to hide every trace of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't normal?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like, why bother going that far?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.74,0:08:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're almost flaunting\ntheir illegal activities at this point,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.83,0:08:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so it seems odd that they would try to hide anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that building, for example.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.91,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even within the Black Market,\nthat bank is notorious for its shady practices.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shady?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I've heard,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.92,0:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,nearly fifteen percent of all the money that funds\ncriminal activity in Kivotos flows through that bank.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.51,0:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The proceeds from crimes like\nembezzlement, robberies, and kidnappings
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.35,0:09:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,are invested into weapons and equipment\nto commit more crime.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.15,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a vicious cycle.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.52,0:09:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wouldn't that mean the bank is complicit?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.28,0:09:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the thing. Even the banks here\nare criminal organisations.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.95,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Market Guard!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Market Guard?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.42,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the elite of the security forces here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're escorting that vehicle.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a cash transport.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.06,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who always collects our money?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patience.\nHere is this month's collection.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job{! Media}.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please sign here?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.86,0:09:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.20,0:09:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kaiser Loans has ties with that bank?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you say Kaiser Loans?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know them, Hifumi{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.16,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, they're the loan sharks run by\nthe infamous Kaiser Corporation, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they a bad company?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.05,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.13,0:10:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kaiser Group is a conglomerate known\nfor skirting the line of legality.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.39,0:10:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They definitely don't sound\nlike the cleanest business.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.35,0:10:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you borrow money from Kaiser Loans?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.31,0:10:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that. It's a long story.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.40,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why they only accept cash payments.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.44,0:10:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've been trying to avoid leaving a paper trail.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.11,0:10:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the money\nwas going to a bank for criminals.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.24,0:10:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean our money has been\nfunding criminals this whole time?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We don't know that for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.41,0:10:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any direct proof that Kaiser Loans\nhas been taking {\i1}our{\i0} money to the Black Market bank.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They should have some kind of receipt\nthat says where the money came from.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can get that,\nwouldn't that count as evidence?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.97,0:10:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.30,0:11:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, on second thought, they probably\nalready took those documents inside,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's too late to get them.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.19,0:11:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with a bank that has top-notch security,\neven by Black Market standards, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this calls for my plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Your plan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.24,0:11:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}that{\i0} one!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. That might be just what we need!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you can't seriously mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.46,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not thinking what I'm thinking, r-right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm sorry, I'm not sure I follow.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.84,0:11:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our only option.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We rob the bank.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.72,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko, hold on! There's gotta be another—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.85,0:11:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.77,0:11:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just finding evidence of their crimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.27,0:11:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you put it like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Copy that.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt anything I say would change your minds.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, what's...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hifumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.90,0:12:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't plan far enough ahead,\nso I don't have a mask prepared for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, am I a part of this now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't just leave you out in the cold like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.79,0:12:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O-On the contrary, I'd much rather you did!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Hifumi{**-chan}. This one's for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, we can talk this out!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.92,0:12:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,shenan,{\clip(m 543 1051 l 868 1032 1031 1009 1229 960 1353 917 1402 1048)}W-Wait, we can talk this out!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.96,0:12:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,shenan,{\clip(m 543 1051 l 868 1032 1028 1014 b 1079 1000 1178 976 1245 958 l 1373 916 1402 1048)}W-Wait, we can talk this out!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.17,0:12:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nono—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.22,0:12:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks super duper cute on you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.68,0:12:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do I really have to do this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.06,0:12:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you do, Hifumi{**-chan}.\nYou promised, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you'd help us find what we're looking for.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.98,0:12:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How am I supposed to explain this\nto the Tea Party if they find out?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.28,0:12:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be A-okay!\nWe're the good guys here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.33,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't ignore the chance that your money\nis being used for malicious purposes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.46,0:12:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Masked Swimsuit Gang!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.34,0:12:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,shenan,{\iclip(636,973,965,1071)}Masked Swimsuit Gang!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.38,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,shenan,{\clip(965,930,1284,1041)\t(0,330,\clip(965,930,1284,1041))}Masked Swimsuit Gang!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.71,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,shenan,{\clip(965,930,1123,1041)\t(0,50,\clip(965,930,1123,1041))}Masked Swimsuit Gang!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Roll out!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.64,0:13:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've just about run out.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.85,0:13:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's it gonna be?\nI need money, and I need it now.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.19,0:13:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, but we are unable\nto process your request at this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.78,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? You mean you can't lend us the money?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.70,0:13:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.99,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an entire office\nand everything! What's the issue?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.66,0:13:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your office is leased.\nThe only tangible assets you own are firearms.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't possibly extend a loan\nunder these circumstances.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.21,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.46,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had collateral to offer or a solid credit history\nwith our bank, we {\i1}could{\i0} extend a loan to you,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.88,0:13:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but may I suggest you start by finding a day job?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.80,0:13:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,729)}E-Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why, you little...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.43,0:13:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should just grab the money\nand raze this place to the ground.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.14,0:13:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that wouldn't work.\nThis place is full of Black Market Guards.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.15,0:13:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'd never get away.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.03,0:14:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have the guts\nto make an enemy of the Black Market.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I even doing? I'm so pathetic.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.82,0:14:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promised myself I would become\nthe number one outlaw in all of Kivotos.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.41,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But look at me now,\nagonising over stupid things like bank loans...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.42,0:14:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't what I wanted.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.92,0:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to live boldly. To become someone\nwho lives on their own terms. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hard-boiled outlaw.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.64,0:14:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or at least, that was the dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.94,0:14:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.82,0:14:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop your weapons! Get down on the ground!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bank robbers?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.95,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as we say or you'll eat lead!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.95,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, umm... For your own safety,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,please stay calm and get on the ground!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wise guy. She said drop your weapons.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, girls...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.76,0:15:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Make extra sure you don't hurt\nany innocent civilians, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.14,0:15:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right-o. So far, so good.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to phase two, shall we?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.14,0:15:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Faust{**-san}. You're our leader,\nso give us the word!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.02,0:15:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? Y-You mean me? I'm Faust?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.15,0:15:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi{**-s}—I mean, Faust{**-san}, you're the leader!\nIn other words, you're our boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And while we're at it...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Christina, gals!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.99,0:15:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Aren't they those girls?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, from Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.54,0:15:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Should we beat them up?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.67,0:15:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, looks like they're not here for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try anything stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That cash transport just now...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.93,0:15:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, of course. Gold, cash, bonds, anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you whatever you want, so please spare me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.72,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we just want the transport logs.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-That's so cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are these people?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.19,0:16:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How do they have the guts to hit\na Black Market bank of all places?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.90,0:16:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're making it look so easy.\nThey must be professionals!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.03,0:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-They're so badass!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now these guys are {\i0}real{\i1} outlaws!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.37,0:16:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh dear, I think I'm tearing up!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Here it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just take it! Don't kill me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.08,0:16:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro—I mean, Blue Two.\nHave you secured the package?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. It's just...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.88,0:16:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty. Let's make like a tree and skedaddle!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, gang, we're leaving!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.76,0:16:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Adios!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.26,0:16:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm glad no one was hurt. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A-After them!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.14,0:16:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seal off the perimeter!\nNotify the Black Market Guards!
Comment: 10,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Aru noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.06,0:16:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You go, outlaws!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.45,0:16:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're out of the hot zone.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.87,0:16:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck yeah! We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.91,0:16:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel my actions as a teacher are questionable at best.
Comment: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hifumi noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.91,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-chan}, you got the transport logs?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.63,0:17:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What the heck is all this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.67,0:17:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-senpai}, you went for the cash instead?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.09,0:17:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No. The documents are right here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yowza. There's easily a hundred million in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.52,0:17:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! Let's bring it back!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.06,0:17:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika, wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.94,0:17:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? This would really help us pay back—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.06,0:17:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that, Serika{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the heck not?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.07,0:17:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We shed blood, sweat, and tears to earn this money.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.45,0:17:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was all going to that bank run by criminals!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.70,0:17:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,True, if we hadn't done anything,\nthis money would've been used to fund more crime.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.41,0:17:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! What's wrong with stealing from criminals?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.25,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with Serika{**-chan} here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's money that was funding criminal activity.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.51,0:17:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be better if we used it for good instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.22,0:17:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, this much money would go a huge way\ntowards paying off the school's debt!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.06,0:17:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Shiroko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.52,0:18:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No point in asking.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You would say no.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.23,0:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Got me there, Shiroko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.99,0:18:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I've rubbed off on you after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.24,0:18:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What we need is documentation. Not cash.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.45,0:18:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If we cross this line because\nwe're up against criminals,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,then what about next time?\nOr the time after that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.71,0:18:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If we start getting used to this way of thinking,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.13,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think one day we're gonna\ndo something we'll come to regret.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.34,0:18:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't bear to watch\nmy cute little juniors lose their way like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is how we wanted to do things,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.93,0:18:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we coulda just used Nonomi{**-chan}'s\nfancy schmancy gold card from the get-go.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.77,0:18:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But you said we shouldn't...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I remember now!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.07,0:18:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we pay off the debt with someone else's money,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll lose the Abydos we were trying to protect.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take just the documents.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.54,0:19:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.41,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say I know what you're going through,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.21,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel like taking this cash would only lead\nto bigger issues later down the line.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's already caused\nits fair share of trouble, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.72,0:19:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, don't worry! I'm not here to pick a fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's {\i1}she{\i0} doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we shoot her?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.48,0:19:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She says she doesn't wanna fight,\nso I'd rather not just blast her.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.61,0:19:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you could say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.90,0:19:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I watched you rob the bank earlier!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.95,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in and out in a flash.\nI was gripped!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.62,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,True outlaws like you come once in a lifetime!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.37,0:19:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I was blown away.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.54,0:19:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of display is a rarity these days!\nI was shaken to my core!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.13,0:19:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've inspired me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.09,0:19:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep working hard to become a free spirit like you,\nunshackled by any rules or laws!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.30,0:19:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The outlaw of my dreams!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she going on about?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.01,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there you have it, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.89,0:20:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If you would be so kind,\ncould you please tell me your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Our name?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.81,0:20:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, you've got to have a team name,\nor a calling card, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.27,0:20:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I can use to remember\nyour brave exploits today.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.32,0:20:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I totally get what you mean!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.20,0:20:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nonomi{**-senpai}, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're known as...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.33,0:20:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the Masked Swimsuit Gang!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Masked Swimsuit Gang?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.00,0:20:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Whoa! That's so badass!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, ho, ho, and one more ho!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.84,0:20:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A tooth for a tooth.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.34,0:20:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We tread a path none may follow,\nand do so without mercy.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our motto!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-Holy smokes. That's {\i0}awesome{\i1}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.40,0:20:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is going on over there?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.98,0:20:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you've had your fun.\nLet's just get out of here already.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. Adios!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Off we go, riding off into the sunset!
Comment: 10,0:21:01.66,0:21:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hoshino noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.36,0:21:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still the middle of the day.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.45,0:21:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"A path none may follow"...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.25,0:21:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna burn those words into my soul!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.17,0:21:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give up now!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when do we tell her?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hilarious, so definitely not right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.80,0:21:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, what about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.64,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they left it behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.06,0:21:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.06,0:21:27.31,Alt,,0,0,0,,Oooh!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.98,0:21:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean we won't have to skip meals anymore?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.53,0:21:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"A path none may follow"...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should write it down and frame it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.28,0:21:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama} has been talking about nothing but\nthe Masked Swimsuit Gang ever since we got back.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.58,0:21:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Think she'll ever connect the dots?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.58,0:21:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,About that Masked Swimsuit Gang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.84,0:21:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the kids from Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.09,0:21:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.72,0:22:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man! You should see your face!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.97,0:22:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{=16}No... No way!

